---
title: Hawker-Style Beef & Veggie Udon Noodles with Broccoli & Crushed Peanuts
description: You won’t miss an ounce of flavour when you toss everything into one bowl. It’s a must to taste all the goodies in this bowl in one bite, with a bunch of udon noodles to tangle up the veggies and flavourful beef mince. Grab a fork, you don’t want to miss out.

